=head1 DESCRIPTION

The filter on the account ID of the linked account, or any of the
following:

C<MONITORED>: linked accounts that are associated to billing groups.

C<UNMONITORED>: linked accounts that are not associated to billing
groups.

C<Billing Group Arn>: linked accounts that are associated to the
provided Billing Group Arn.

=head1 ATTRIBUTES


=head2 AccountId => Str

The Amazon Web Services account ID to filter on.


=head2 AccountIds => ArrayRef[Str|Undef]

The list of Amazon Web Services IDs to retrieve their associated
billing group for a given time range.


=head2 Association => Str

C<MONITORED>: linked accounts that are associated to billing groups.

C<UNMONITORED>: linked accounts that are not associated to billing
groups.

C<Billing Group Arn>: linked accounts that are associated to the
provided Billing Group Arn.



